track_notes: Park the car at le Col de La Sine, then you must walk 1.5km on a very nice path, witch does not go up at all! When you reach the Col de St Pons (small Church) turn right and climb until no more power left in your legs; it is not very easy to walk as there is no path; but since i climb there winter or summer time the path is getting clear now! on summit it is the place for radio!
No more to say, just behave where you climb
